{"type":"text","timestamp":1782446234827,"sessionID":"ses_0fdf0abbcffeXZ79acy1pUYMV9","part":{"id":"prt_f0212eee5001x0GryZ3bDfHar2","messageID":"msg_f0212d0fd001N6ZdheRROKGzsG","sessionID":"ses_0fdf0abbcffeXZ79acy1pUYMV9","type":"text","text":"Covered the phase-06 verification cluster by fixing the target test package harness and updating the three in-scope matrix rows from harness-blocked evidence to focused test-pass evidence.\n\nChanged files:\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie/cjpm.toml`: added the missing OHOS target `compile-option`/`bin-dependencies` sections so the test package uses the same sysroot/linker setup as the main entry package.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`: updated the 3 phase-06 verification rows in this cluster to record successful focused test evidence instead of the stale linker blocker.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`: synced by `patch_authority.py` after the authority update.\n\nCovered current-phase gate entries:\n- `app-src-androidtest-java-com-example-foodike-exampleinst-7ce120cd33-001-source-side-tests-or-verification-assets`\n  Reconfirmed the source Android test is boilerplate package-name scaffolding and mapped it to focused target behavior tests with passing test evidence.\n- `app-src-test-java-com-example-foodike-exampleunittest-kt-7340d393c5-001-source-side-tests-or-verification-assets`\n  Reconfirmed the source host-side arithmetic example is boilerplate and replaced it with passing target behavior tests.\n- `app-src-test-java-com-example-foodike-exampleunittest-kt-504d70964f-002-crud-mutation-or-persistent-state-update`\n  Kept the concrete mutation endpoints and upgraded verification from harness-blocked to focused-test-pass.\n\nRemaining current-phase gate entries:\n- None within this cluster.\n- The workflow-owned reports under `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-06-polish-tests-verification/` and phase checklist/gate reports are now stale relative to the successful bounded reproduction. I did not rewrite them because they are generated artifacts. They should be refreshed by the normal workflow rerun.\n\nSource paths/clusters handled:\n- Cluster: `cluster-prep-contract-phase-06-polish-tests-verification-verification`\n- Child groups:\n  - `prep-phase-06-polish-tests-verification-phase-06-polish-tests-verification-verification-com-exam`\n  - `prep-phase-06-polish-tests-verification-phase-06-polish-tests-verification-verification-phase-te`\n- Source files:\n  - `app/src/androidTest/java/com/example/foodike/ExampleInstrumentedTest.kt`\n  - `app/src/test/java/com/example/foodike/ExampleUnitTest.kt`\n\nTests added or updated:\n- No new test files were needed; the target already had focused behavior tests:\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj`\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase03_onboarding_login_profile_test.cj`\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj`\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase05_detail_cart_state_mutations_test.cj`\n- Updated test harness config:\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/cjpm.toml`\n\nCommands run:\n- `cjpm.exe test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` from `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie` with the env overlay from the phase-06 test-build report\n- `python.exe D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\source_coverage\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix ...`\n\nBuild result:\n- Phase-06 test reproduction: PASS for the bounded manual reproduction command.\n- Latest workflow report on disk: still shows `TEST_COMPILE_FAIL` and is stale until regenerated.\n\nPlan changes:\n- none\n\nDeferred issues:\n- none for this cluster\n\nOut-of-scope whole-project warnings:\n- `phase-06` still has the broader workflow finding that no critical/high rows are assigned to this phase. That is outside this single verification cluster and was not changed here.\n- There are many unrelated dirty/generated workspace changes already present. I left them untouched.\n\nNext recommended action:\n1.